<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٥١]</span> سورة البقرة <span class="c2">(١٢٥،١٢٧،١٥٨)</span> وآل عمران <span class="c2">(٩٦،٩٧)</span> ، والأنفال <span class="c2">(٣٥)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
